  "pageTitle": "Construction waste crusher and screening plant for recycled aggregate",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page product-page-industrial\">\n      <section class=\"section split-section\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Turnkey C&D Waste Recycling Plant</p>\n          <h1>Construction waste crusher and screening plant for recycled aggregate</h1>\n          <p class=\"hero-copy\">The WEI LAN Lion One system combines crushing, trommel screening, vibrating screening, magnetic separation, air separation, baling, weighing, and digital control for construction waste, decoration waste, demolition waste, and bulky waste projects.</p>\n          <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n            <a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/contact\">Request Proposal</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <picture>\n          <img src=\"/assets/images/lion-mark1.jpg\" alt=\"Integrated construction waste crushing and screening station\">\n        </picture>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\" id=\"core-parameters\" aria-labelledby=\"core-parameters-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Core parameters</p>\n          <h2 id=\"core-parameters-title\">Lion One integrated crushing &amp; screening station</h2>\n          <p>Heavy-duty mobile station designed for construction, decoration, demolition, and bulky waste streams. All four core parameters are listed in their working ranges.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"spec-group spec-group-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"core-parameters-title\">\n          <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-wide\">\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-industrial\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">L1</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">Lion One</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">Integrated crushing &amp; screening station</p>\n                </div>\n                <dl class=\"spec-card-plate\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <div><dt>MFG</dt><dd>WEI&nbsp;LAN</dd></div>\n                  <div><dt>TYPE</dt><dd>MOBILE&nbsp;STATION</dd></div>\n                  <div><dt>GRADE</dt><dd>HEAVY&nbsp;DUTY</dd></div>\n                </dl>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics spec-metrics-wide\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>Capacity</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">20&ndash;70</span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-suffix-unit\">t/h</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>Feed size</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">200</span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-suffix-unit\">mm</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>Footprint</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">35</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\"><span class=\"spec-suffix-unit\">m<sup>2</sup></span> &middot; 11.7 &times; 3 &times; 3.1 m</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>Drive</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">100<small>%</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">full hydraulic</span></dd>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n              <footer class=\"spec-card-foot\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-mark\">WEI LAN</span>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span>\n                <span>Ningbo, China</span>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span>\n                <span>Integrated Mobile Station</span>\n              </footer>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Line Modules</p>\n          <h2>Compact footprint with complete resource recovery process</h2>\n          <p>Configured for recycled aggregate recovery, light material separation, metal removal, automated control, and operational reporting.</p>\n        </div>\n        <ol class=\"industrial-ledger\" role=\"list\">\n          <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-01</span>\n            <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\">\n              <h3>Lion One station</h3>\n              <p>Integrated crushing and screening station with 200 mm feed size, 35 m<sup>2</sup> footprint, and full hydraulic drive.</p>\n            </div>\n            <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\">\n              <div><dt>Feed</dt><dd>200 mm</dd></div>\n              <div><dt>Drive</dt><dd>Hydraulic</dd></div>\n            </dl>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-02</span>\n            <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\">\n              <h3>20-70 t/h options</h3>\n              <p>Capacity options fit different municipal, industrial, and construction waste resource utilization projects.</p>\n            </div>\n            <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\">\n              <div><dt>Range</dt><dd>20-70 t/h</dd></div>\n              <div><dt>Tiers</dt><dd>3 grades</dd></div>\n            </dl>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-03</span>\n            <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\">\n              <h3>Separation modules</h3>\n              <p>Supports shredder, trommel screen for construction waste, vibrating screen for recycled aggregate, magnetic separator for C&D waste, positive-negative pressure air separation system for construction waste, and baler.</p>\n            </div>\n            <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\">\n              <div><dt>Modules</dt><dd>6 stages</dd></div>\n              <div><dt>Config</dt><dd>Modular</dd></div>\n            </dl>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"industrial-ledger-row\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-ledger-tag\">M-04</span>\n            <div class=\"industrial-ledger-body\">\n              <h3>PLC and DCS control</h3>\n              <p>Manual, automatic, and remote control modes support start-stop control, alerts, weighing flow, and reporting.</p>\n            </div>\n            <dl class=\"industrial-ledger-spec\">\n              <div><dt>Modes</dt><dd>Manual · Auto · Remote</dd></div>\n              <div><dt>Control</dt><dd>PLC + DCS</dd></div>\n            </dl>\n          </li>\n        </ol>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section dark-section product-process-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-process-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Process Overview</p>\n          <h2 id=\"construction-process-title\">C&amp;D waste flow from mixed input to reusable output</h2>\n          <p>The construction waste line turns mixed C&amp;D material into reusable output through controlled feeding, crushing, screening, and final recovery handling.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"industrial-flow\" aria-label=\"Construction waste recycling process\">\n          <div class=\"industrial-flow-track\">\n            <article class=\"industrial-flow-node\">\n              <span class=\"industrial-flow-rank\">01</span>\n              <h3>Feeding</h3>\n              <p>Receive construction, decoration, demolition, or bulky waste into the integrated processing line.</p>\n              <figure class=\"industrial-flow-media\" aria-label=\"Feeding video placeholder\">\n                <div class=\"industrial-flow-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Video coming soon\">\n                  <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-tag\">CAM-01</span>\n                  <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"industrial-flow-node\">\n              <span class=\"industrial-flow-rank\">02</span>\n              <h3>Crushing</h3>\n              <p>Reduce mixed waste into a more manageable particle size for downstream screening and separation.</p>\n              <figure class=\"industrial-flow-media\" aria-label=\"Crushing video placeholder\">\n                <div class=\"industrial-flow-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Video coming soon\">\n                  <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-tag\">CAM-02</span>\n                  <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"industrial-flow-node\">\n              <span class=\"industrial-flow-rank\">03</span>\n              <h3>Screening</h3>\n              <p>Separate material by size to support aggregate recovery and cleaner downstream processing.</p>\n              <figure class=\"industrial-flow-media\" aria-label=\"Screening video placeholder\">\n                <div class=\"industrial-flow-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Video coming soon\">\n                  <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-tag\">CAM-03</span>\n                  <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"industrial-flow-wrap\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-flow-wrap-down\"></span>\n            <span class=\"industrial-flow-wrap-arrow\"></span>\n          </div>\n          <article class=\"industrial-flow-node industrial-flow-finale\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-flow-rank\">04</span>\n            <p class=\"industrial-flow-finale-eyebrow\">Output</p>\n            <h3>Recycled output</h3>\n            <p>Produce recycled aggregates and reusable fractions ready for downstream reuse.</p>\n            <figure class=\"industrial-flow-media\" aria-label=\"Recycled output video placeholder\">\n              <div class=\"industrial-flow-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Video coming soon\">\n                <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-tag\">CAM-04</span>\n                <span class=\"industrial-flow-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              </div>\n            </figure>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section product-compare-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-compare-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Product Comparison</p>\n          <h2 id=\"construction-compare-title\">Lion One vs. MK-F50</h2>\n          <p>How the WEI LAN integrated C&amp;D waste line stacks up against a typical multi-machine site setup on the metrics that drive total cost of ownership.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"product-compare-layout\">\n          <figure class=\"product-compare-explode\" aria-label=\"Lion One exploded view\">\n            <div class=\"product-compare-explode-frame\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Exploded view diagram coming soon\">\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-tag\">EXPLODED · LION ONE</span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:18%;--pin-y:32%\" data-label=\"01\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:38%;--pin-y:58%\" data-label=\"02\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:58%;--pin-y:26%\" data-label=\"03\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:74%;--pin-y:64%\" data-label=\"04\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:88%;--pin-y:40%\" data-label=\"05\"></span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-label\">Exploded view coming soon</span>\n            </div>\n            <figcaption>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-explode-meta\">Integrated mobile station · heavy duty</span>\n            </figcaption>\n          </figure>\n\n          <div class=\"product-compare-panel\">\n            <header class=\"product-compare-panel-head\">\n              <span class=\"product-compare-legend\">\n                <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-self\"></span>WEI LAN Lion One\n              </span>\n              <span class=\"product-compare-legend\">\n                <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-base\"></span>GREATWALL HAVEY INDUSTRY MK-F50\n              </span>\n            </header>\n\n            <ul class=\"product-compare-list\" role=\"list\">\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-01</span>\n                  <h3>Footprint</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">m² for the integrated station</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:79%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">35 m²</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">44.2 m²</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">Integrated mobile station replaces a multi-machine yard layout in a single skid.</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-02</span>\n                  <h3>Capacity</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">t/h rated range</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">20-70 t/h</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:88.6%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">40-62 t/h</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">Capacity bars are scaled by upper rated throughput on the 70 t/h ceiling, while the labels keep each model's full operating range.</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-03</span>\n                  <h3>Power draw</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">kW per 100 t/h</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:80%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">132 kW</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">165 kW</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">Roughly 25% lower power per tonne sorted, calculated at rated throughput.</p>\n              </li>\n\n              <li class=\"product-compare-row\">\n                <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\">\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-04</span>\n                  <h3>Transport &amp; assembly</h3>\n                  <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">days to commission</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-compare-bars\">\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:12%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">Lion One</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">2–3 days</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:95%\">\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">MK-F50</span>\n                    <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">18 – 25 days</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">Mobile station ships on standard trailers; on-site work is positioning and hookup only.</p>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section industrial-faq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-faq-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">FAQ</p>\n          <h2 id=\"construction-faq-title\">C&amp;D waste recycling plant questions before project sizing</h2>\n          <p>Use these answers to prepare early supplier comparison, internal feasibility review, and RFQ information for construction waste recycling equipment.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"industrial-faq-panel\">\n          <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-01</span>\n            <div>\n              <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">What affects C&amp;D waste recycling plant cost?</h3>\n              <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">Cost depends on target capacity, feed size, required output, crusher and screening scope, magnetic separation, air separation, baling, control system, site layout, and commissioning support.</p>\n              <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n                <span class=\"faq-input-label\">Required inputs</span>\n                <span>Target capacity</span>\n                <span>Site layout</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-02</span>\n            <div>\n              <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">What materials can the construction waste line process?</h3>\n              <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">The line is built for construction waste, decoration waste, demolition waste, bulky waste, and mixed light materials that need crushing, screening, metal recovery, and light-heavy separation.</p>\n              <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n                <span class=\"faq-input-label\">Required inputs</span>\n                <span>Waste composition</span>\n                <span>Material photos or videos</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-03</span>\n            <div>\n              <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">Which equipment modules are usually included?</h3>\n              <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">A typical line may include feeding, crushing, trommel screening, vibrating screening, magnetic separator for C&amp;D waste, air separation system, baler, weighing, PLC control, and remote monitoring.</p>\n              <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n                <span class=\"faq-input-label\">Required inputs</span>\n                <span>Required output specification</span>\n                <span>Recovery modules needed</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"industrial-faq-item\">\n            <span class=\"industrial-faq-code\">RFQ-04</span>\n            <div>\n              <h3 class=\"industrial-faq-question\">How should buyers choose the right capacity?</h3>\n              <p class=\"industrial-faq-answer\">Capacity should be matched to hourly input, material density, expected uptime, output specification, local transport flow, and site footprint. WEI LAN can review project data before recommending a 20-70 t/h configuration.</p>\n              <div class=\"faq-input-list\">\n                <span class=\"faq-input-label\">Required inputs</span>\n                <span>Feed size</span>\n                <span>Operating hours and uptime</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section industrial-rfq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-rfq-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">RFQ preparation</p>\n          <h2 id=\"construction-rfq-title\">Prepare the data package for C&amp;D line quotation</h2>\n          <p>Use this checklist to prepare enough engineering context for capacity selection, module configuration, transport planning, and installation review.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"industrial-rfq-checklist\">\n          <article>\n            <span>DATA-01</span>\n            <h3>Waste composition</h3>\n            <p>Estimate concrete, brick, wood, plastic, metal, soil, decoration waste, bulky waste, and light impurity proportions.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>DATA-02</span>\n            <h3>Feed size</h3>\n            <p>Confirm maximum incoming size, average lump size, pre-sorting condition, and whether oversize material needs pre-crushing.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>DATA-03</span>\n            <h3>Target capacity</h3>\n            <p>Share hourly throughput, working shifts, expected uptime, seasonal load changes, and required final aggregate specification.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span>DATA-04</span>\n            <h3>Site layout</h3>\n            <p>Provide available footprint, truck movement path, power access, water and dust-control limits, and discharge storage zones.</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rfq-action-strip\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">Request Engineering Review</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/resources\">Prepare File Pack</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
